data.name: Speech Assistant
data.desc: Speech Assistant is designed to help individuals with speech impairments communicate effectively. Simply type text, and the app will convert it into clear speech using Text-to-Speech (TTS) technology. You can easily play the TTS output, add new text, and hear it instantly. Whether you need quick communication on the go or a reliable speech aid, this app provides an intuitive, accessible solution for everyday use.
